@startuml Sequence_Comment
title Sequence Diagram - Bình luận bài học (UC6)

actor User as U
participant "Lesson Page" as V
participant "CommentController" as CMC
participant "CommentService" as CMS
database "Database" as DB

== Tải danh sách Comment ==
U -> V : Xem trang Lesson
V -> CMC : GET /lesson/{id}/comments
CMC -> CMS : getCommentsByLessonId(lessonId)
CMS -> DB : SELECT c.*, u.username, u.avatar_url\nFROM comments c\nJOIN users u ON c.user_id = u.id\nWHERE c.lesson_id = ?\nORDER BY c.created_at DESC
DB --> CMS : List<Comment>
CMS -> CMS : Sắp xếp theo thread\n(parent_id → replies)
CMS --> CMC : List<Comment> (threaded)
CMC --> V : Render comments
V --> U : Hiển thị comments

== Viết Comment mới ==
U -> V : Nhập nội dung comment
V -> CMC : POST /comment\n{content, lessonId}
CMC -> CMS : createComment(content, lessonId, userId)
CMS -> DB : INSERT INTO comments\n(content, lesson_id, user_id,\nparent_id = NULL, created_at)
DB --> CMS : Saved Comment
CMS --> CMC : Comment
CMC --> V : Comment mới
V --> U : Hiển thị comment vừa tạo

== Reply Comment ==
U -> V : Nhấn Reply trên comment
U -> V : Nhập nội dung reply
V -> CMC : POST /comment\n{content, lessonId, parentId}
CMC -> CMS : createComment(content, lessonId, userId, parentId)
CMS -> DB : INSERT INTO comments\n(content, lesson_id, user_id,\nparent_id = ?, created_at)
DB --> CMS : Saved Comment
CMS --> CMC : Reply Comment
CMC --> V : Reply mới
V --> U : Hiển thị reply dưới comment gốc

@enduml
